Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
reset_ideal_network(25.10)                          reset_ideal_network(25.10)

Name
       reset_ideal_network  -  Resets the ideal network constraints, specified
       using the set_ideal_network command, on pins, ports, or nets

Syntax
       reset_ideal_network

       [-help]

       <object_list>

       Resets   the   ideal   network   constraints,   specified   using   the
       set_ideal_network command, on pins, ports, or nets.

       Note:  The  reset_ideal_network command applies to all the active views
       and is not view/mode-based.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       <object_list>
              Resets a list of objects - instance pins, ports, or nets.

Related Information
       set_ideal_network

